sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    actor Target as Banned User
    participant fe@{ "type": "boundary" } as Admin Panel
    participant API@{ "type": "control" } as API
    participant db@{ "type": "database" } as Database
    participant mw@{ "type": "control" } as checkBanned Middleware

    Note over Admin,db: Phase 1 — Admin issues ban

    Admin->>+fe: Select user → "Ban" (reason, optional expiresAt)
    fe->>+API: PATCH /admin/users/:id/ban { banReason, banExpiresAt }
    API->>API: verifyToken + isAdmin

    API->>+db: user.findUnique(id)
    db-->>-API: user or null

    alt User missing
        API-->>fe: 404 "User not found."
        fe-->>Admin: Show error
    else User found
        API->>+db: user.update(<br/>bannedAt = now (if not already set),<br/>banReason, banExpiresAt)
        db-->>-API: Updated
        API-->>fe: 200 "Banned <fullName>"
        fe-->>-Admin: Refresh user list
    end

    Note over Target,mw: Phase 2 — Banned user hits a protected route

    Target->>API: Any request to a route using checkBanned
    API->>+mw: verifyToken passes, run checkBanned
    mw->>+db: user.findUnique(id, select ban fields)
    db-->>-mw: user (with bannedAt, banExpiresAt, banReason)

    alt bannedAt set AND (no expiry OR expiry in future)
        mw-->>API: 403 with banDetails
        API-->>Target: 403 "Your account is banned." + banDetails
    else Not banned (or ban expired)
        mw->>mw: Attach req.dbUser
        mw-->>-API: next()
        API-->>Target: Continue normal handler
    end

    Note over Admin,db: Phase 3 — Admin unbans

    Admin->>+fe: Click "Unban" on user
    fe->>+API: PATCH /admin/users/:id/unban
    API->>API: verifyToken + isAdmin
    API->>+db: user.findUnique(id)
    db-->>-API: user or null

    alt User missing or not currently banned
        API-->>fe: 400 "User is either not banned or not found"
        fe-->>Admin: Show error
    else Banned user
        API->>+db: user.update(<br/>bannedAt=null, banReason=null, banExpiresAt=null)
        db-->>-API: Updated
        API-->>fe: 200 "Unbanned <fullName>"
        fe-->>-Admin: Refresh list
    end
